AI Appointment Scheduler
Schedule Google Calendar appointments effortlessly using natural language.

Features
# Natural Language Input: Describe appointments like "Meeting with John tomorrow at 3 PM."
# AI-Powered: Uses Gemini AI to extract event details.
# Google Calendar Integration: Creates events directly in your calendar.
# Smart Date/Time: Handles relative dates and past time adjustments.
Setup
# Google Credentials: Get credentials.json from Google Cloud Console (enable Google Calendar API, create OAuth 2.0 Client ID for Desktop app).
# Gemini API Key: Get your Gemini API key from Google AI Studio.
# .env File: Create a .env file in the same directory as app.py with Gemini-API="YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE".
# Install: pip install streamlit google-api-python-client google-auth-oauthlib google-auth-httplib2 python-dotenv langchain-google-genai
